<main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 py-12 space-y-12">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">Liquid Staking</h1>

  <p>Liquid staking involves issuing a token that represents a staked asset. This token can be used in other applications.</p>

  <section class="space-y-6">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">What is Liquid Staking?</h2>
    <p>Liquid staking addresses the liquidity limitations of traditional staking by allowing users to stake their assets while retaining the ability to use them elsewhere. This is achieved through tokenized representations of the staked assets, providing flexibility and enhanced capital efficiency.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="space-y-6">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">How Does Liquid Staking Work?</h2>
    <p>When users stake their assets via a liquid staking protocol, they receive a token that represents their staked position... These tokens can be traded, used in DeFi, or even <a href="/restaking" class="text-blue-600 underline">restaked</a>.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="space-y-6">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Advantages of Liquid Staking</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Maintained Liquidity</strong>: Users can utilize their staked assets without waiting for unbonding periods.</li>
      <li><strong>Enhanced Capital Efficiency</strong>: Tokenized staked assets can be deployed in various DeFi strategies.</li>
      <li><strong>Flexibility</strong>: Participants can switch between providers or strategies easily.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="space-y-6">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Challenges of Liquid Staking</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Smart Contract Risks</strong>: Complex smart contracts introduce vulnerabilities.</li>
      <li><strong>Price Volatility</strong>: Token values may not align with underlying assets.</li>
      <li><strong>Centralization Concerns</strong>: Large providers could reduce network decentralization.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Liquid staking offers a solution for those seeking staking rewards without sacrificing liquidity...</p>
  </section>

